'''Tutlayin titergiyin''' (s [[Tutlayt tamaceɣt|tmaceɣt]]: '''ⵜⴰⵓⴰⵏⵏⵜ ⵜⴰⵏ ⵜⵎⴰⵛⵈ''' neɣ '''ⵜⴰⵎⴰⵌⵈ''') d afurk seg tegrawt n [[tutlayin timaziɣin]] s wacu ttmeslayen [[Imuhaɣ]] deg [[Aneẓruf Ameqran|Uneẓruf Ameqran]], dɣa d tutlayin-a kan i mazal ggẓent (ḥerzent) talɣa n tira n [[agemmay|ugemmay]] Tifinaɣ-Aliban yettusemman daɣen [[tifinaɣ]] tamzikt. 

Llant kuẓ n tutlayin titergiyin ('''[[Tutlayt tamajeɣt|Tayirt]]''', '''[[Tutlayt tamaceɣt|Tamaceɣt]]''', '''[[Tutlayt Tamahaq|Tamahaɣt]]''', '''[[Tutlayt tawellemt|Tawellemt]]''') ttmeslayen yisen-tt ugar n 5 n imelyan n itergiyen di tmura n [[Nnijer|Nijer]], [[Libya]], [[Lezzayer]], [[Mali]] yakk d [[Burkina Faso]]. Akken i llant kra n tɣerfin n itergiyen yettidiren di [[Ččad]] d [[Tunes]] d [[Nijirya]] d [[Sudan]].

== Addad ==

Tatergit tettemgerrad deg tama ɣer tayeḍ. Tatergit n [[Ahaggar|Uhaggaṛ]] (tin umi ɣɣaren tahaggaṛt neɣ tamaheɣt), ssawalen-tt deg wenẓul n Lezzayer. Tamaceq ssawalen-tt deg [[Mali]] g [[Aẓawad|Uẓawad]], ma d tamajeq/tayirt ssawalen-tt deg [[Nnijer]]. Tutlayt-a mazal tettwaru ar ass-a s ugemmay n tfinaɣ, maca, deg Nnijer ed Mali, llan wid ay tt-yettarun s ugemmay alatini. Tamaceɣt ssawalen-tt daɣen deg [[Libya]] akekd Burkina Faso, am wakken ay llan cwiṭ n Yimuhaɣ deg [[Nijirya]] d [[Ččad]].

